reviewText: I bought this DVD hoping to learn more about the F-16. But it is actually a well put together presentation of Aviation history up to the F-16 but very little is mentioned about my favorite fighter jet.

DO NOT BE FOOLED WITH THE TITLE OR DESCRIPTION OF THIS DVD. IT HAS NOTHING TO DO WITH THE F-16!!!!! IN FACT, THERE IS ONLY ABOUT 15 SECONDS OF FOOTAGE AND TALK OF THE F-16. WORST DVD I'VE EVER BOUGHT!!!! DO NOT WASTE YOUR MONEY!!!!
